document_data.History:
In 1489 DR, two newly hired scribes, [[Spernik]] and [[Tibeem]], were discovered stealing books from the Lord's private chambers. Tibeem killed one of the summoned [[Knights of the Black Fist]] and was captured, but Spernik escaped. So the Lord Sage hired an adventuring party to find the thief and the stolen books.{{Cite adventurers league/The Courting of Fire|7-8}} After the coup of [[Vorgansharax]] in conjuration with [[Harpers]] he sent adventurers to explore the [[Yarash]]'s pyramid.{{Cite adventurers league/Dark Pyramid of Sorcerer's Isle|7}}

Later Vorgansharax trapped the Lord Sage inside his library in Phlan but he knew too much.{{Cite adventurers league/Escape from Phlan|7}}
Thank to an adventuring party hired by the resistance he managed to escape [[Phlan]].{{Cite adventurers league/Escape from Phlan|13-17}}
